    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【抢先体验】《Orbcraft Survivors》仍在开发中。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Orbcraft Survivors</strong> 是一款结合了<strong>Roguelite元素</strong>的<strong>时间生存游戏</strong>，在其中你可以打造宝珠并赋予强力特性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合成相同的球体</strong>以强化为更强大的形态，<strong>获取、组合并应用特性</strong>以最大化效果。尝试不同组合，释放<strong>压倒性的魔法</strong>，并在敌人的冲击中生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/dc168cc9444a20e3ffec30c500eb860c.avif?t=1770802344\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras_big/dc168cc9444a20e3ffec30c500eb860c.avif?t=1770802344 width=800 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位角色最多可装备<strong>6个以上宝珠</strong>，每颗宝珠皆具独特技能。合成以增强它们，并<strong>释放3级宝珠</strong>主导战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/6a49b96119a0712e3c3d32e7e4fd514f.poster.avif?t=1770802344\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/6a49b96119a0712e3c3d32e7e4fd514f.webm?t=1770802344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/6a49b96119a0712e3c3d32e7e4fd514f.mp4?t=1770802344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/26d618d4dcaf64046e7291294279d196.avif?t=1770802344\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras_big/26d618d4dcaf64046e7291294279d196.avif?t=1770802344 width=800 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有<strong>超过100种特性组合</strong>，每场战斗都能尝试新策略。发现强力协同，<strong>测试你的运气和策略</strong>，每一局都与众不同！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/c9f19c5f3826eaef4cfc12457a5b0c8d.poster.avif?t=1770802344\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/c9f19c5f3826eaef4cfc12457a5b0c8d.webm?t=1770802344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/c9f19c5f3826eaef4cfc12457a5b0c8d.mp4?t=1770802344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/ae452aa7eccfcefc3ea1b92942ff30d2.avif?t=1770802344\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras_big/ae452aa7eccfcefc3ea1b92942ff30d2.avif?t=1770802344 width=800 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在正确的时机<strong>运用每位角色的独特技能</strong>，收集金币以解锁<strong>强大天赋</strong>，充分释放角色潜力。精明投资，突破极限，成为最后的生还者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/b104e8d16f8a2f13f7b8e20789f9ec09.poster.avif?t=1770802344\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/b104e8d16f8a2f13f7b8e20789f9ec09.webm?t=1770802344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327240/extras/b104e8d16f8a2f13f7b8e20789f9ec09.mp4?t=1770802344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
